This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and focuses on paraphrase generation, which is a common task in NLP. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves the use of machine learning models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also evaluates the performance of models using standard metrics, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with language generation and could be relevant to information retrieval, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
